    User Engagement with Upcoming Title

    As a curious visitor, I explore more about the upcoming title 'Cursed Crown', so that I can stay updated about the game and anticipate its release.

    Success definition: Given I am on the Glade Studio website When I click on the ABOUT link and then the 'Learn more' link on the about page Then I should see the details about 'Cursed Crown', including the heading 'Trailer coming soon!' And when I click on the 'Watch trailer' link, the page should scroll to the trailer section with updated navigation links.
